  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/e46f5148f7e91bd5ec86f46bf582db08.poster.avif?t=1591631506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/e46f5148f7e91bd5ec86f46bf582db08.webm?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/e46f5148f7e91bd5ec86f46bf582db08.mp4?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Switchblade is a completely free arena-based 5v5 vehicular shooter that combines high-octane combat with an ever-shifting array of strategic choices. Seamlessly switch between heavily armed vehicles at any time to create endless tactical choices.<br><br>Switchblade is in Early Access and may have bugs and balance issues.<br><br>In-game purchases optional<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/4124ec57616898f66ad82ad409aab30c.poster.avif?t=1591631506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/4124ec57616898f66ad82ad409aab30c.webm?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/4124ec57616898f66ad82ad409aab30c.mp4?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/e46f5148f7e91bd5ec86f46bf582db08.poster.avif?t=1591631506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/e46f5148f7e91bd5ec86f46bf582db08.webm?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/e46f5148f7e91bd5ec86f46bf582db08.mp4?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Switchblade is a completely free arena-based 5v5 vehicular shooter that combines high-octane combat with an ever-shifting array of strategic choices. Seamlessly switch between heavily armed vehicles at any time to create endless tactical choices.<br><br>Switchblade is in Early Access and may have bugs and balance issues.<br><br>In-game purchases optional<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/4124ec57616898f66ad82ad409aab30c.poster.avif?t=1591631506\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/4124ec57616898f66ad82ad409aab30c.webm?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/585630/extras/4124ec57616898f66ad82ad409aab30c.mp4?t=1591631506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
